---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Rithika Silva - Uses" description="A list of hardware and software I use daily.">
  <main class="mt-20 text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6">
    <a href="/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-100 mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back</a>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">What I Use</h1>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 border-gray-400 pb-2 mb-6">Hardware</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Tachyon - ASUS ROG Zephyrus G14 (2022)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">AMD Ryzen 9 6900HS, Radeon RX 6700S, 16GB RAM, 1TB SSD</p>
          <p class="mt-2">My main personal computer. I dual boot Fedora for work and school, using Hyprland as my desktop environment, and Windows 11 for gaming only.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Maelstrom - Lenovo M900 Tiny</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Intel i5-6500T, 16GB DDR4 RAM, 500GB Samsung 860 Evo SSD, Ubuntu Server</p>
          <p class="mt-2">A lightweight server for remote storage and services like NTFY.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Typhoon - Dell Optiplex 360</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Pentium 35200, 4GB DDR3 RAM, 256GB SSD, Ubuntu Server</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Recently decommissioned. Used to be another lightweight server.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Ion - iPhone 16</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">128GB</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Daily driver phone.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Positron - 3rd Gen M1 iPad Pro (11 inch)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">128GB</p>
          <p class="mt-2">It's been great for classes, I mostly use it for handwriting notes with my Apple Pencil.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 border-gray-400 pb-2 mb-6">Accessories</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Libtery - ROG Falchion Ace</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">All-black blank keycaps, ROG NX Brown switches, Glorious Coiled Aviator Cable</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Preferred keyboard when at a desk.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Razer Viper V3</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">For when it's time to game.</p>
        </li>
        
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Apple Watch Series 10</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Black, GPS only</p>
          <p class="mt-2">An all-around great smartwatch.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 border-gray-400 pb-2 mb-6">Audio Gear</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Shokz Open Run Pro 2</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">Great for those that sweat easily.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Sony WH-1000XM4</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">My favorite pair of headphones ever.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 border-gray-400 pb-2 mb-6">Software</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Neovim</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">My text editor of choice. I use it for everything.</p>
        </li>
        
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Tmux</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">A terminal multiplexer that allows me to manage multiple terminal sessions. I have a setup similar to <a href="https://github.com/ThePrimeagen/tmux-sessionizer" target="_blank" class="italic text-white hover:underline">ThePrimeagen</a>.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Kitty</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">A fast, feature-rich, GPU based terminal emulator.</p>
        </li>
        
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Typst</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">A new markup-based typesetting system, a modern alternative to LaTeX.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Todoist</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">For managing tasks and staying organized.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Google Calendar</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">For scheduling and managing my time.</p>
        </li>
        
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Iosevka Font</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">My preferred monospace font for coding and terminal use.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Firefox</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">My primary web browser.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold border-b-2 border-gray-400 pb-2 mb-6">Photography Gear</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Sony ZV-E10</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">My primary camera for photos and videos.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Sony 50MM F1.8 Lens</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">My go-to lens.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Sony 16-50MM F3.5-5.6 Lens</h3>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-100">Meta Ray-Bans</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Wayfarer frame</p>
          <p class="mt-2">For hands-free photo and video capture.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
